    {
      "id": "detailed_2_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_2",
      "description": "This vehicle is in fair condition and serves as a reliable daily driver, though it is not without its imperfections. Mechanically, it runs and drives well, but you should expect some minor leaks and typical wear on the suspension components. The exterior shows some noticeable scratches and fading paint, while the interior has visible wear on the upholstery. It\u2019s a solid, functional car for someone who prioritizes utility over aesthetics.",
