    {
      "id": "optimistic_5_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "optimistic_5",
      "description": "Looking for a budget-friendly project or a reliable source of parts? This vehicle is ready for a dedicated new owner! It shows significant wear and will require some mechanical attention and TLC to get back to its best, but it offers a fantastic opportunity for a mechanic or a DIY enthusiast to roll up their sleeves. Grab this diamond in the rough at a great price and make it your own!",
