    },
    {
      "id": "detailed_3_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_3",
      "description": "This vehicle is being sold in poor condition and currently does not run. The engine requires a complete overhaul or replacement, and the transmission shows signs of severe slipping. The exterior has several large dents and significant rust patches along the rocker panels, while the interior shows heavy wear and tear with torn upholstery. This is strictly a project car or parts vehicle for someone with the mechanical expertise to address major failures.",
